UNITED STATES of America, Respondent, v. Frank GALASEK, Appellant. No. 110. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 18, 1935. John K. Gerken, of Buffalo, N. Y., for appellant. George L. Grobe, U. S. Atty., of Buffalo, N. Y. (Robert M. Hitchcock, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for the United States.

. Before MANTON, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
